Description copied from interface: AnnotationHandler
This method should provide the logic for feature extraction and annotation updating/creating based on classifier results. Typically, this method will iterate through annotations in the cas, extract features, and then call consumer.consume() or consumer.consumeAll() for each instance or group of instances to be processed.
